            "text": "Z c (3900)",
            "section_rank": 1
        },
        {
            "text": "Photoproduction Tetraquark A search for the exclusive production of the Z \u00b1 c (3900) hadron by virtual photons has been performed in the channel Z \u00b1 c (3900) \u2192 J /\u03c8\u03c0 \u00b1 . ",
            "section": "Z c (3900)",
            "paragraph_rank": 2,
            "section_rank": 1
        },
        {
            "text": "The data cover the range from 7 GeV to 19 GeV in the centreof-mass energy of the photon-nucleon system. ",
            "section": "Z c (3900)",
            "paragraph_rank": 2,
            "section_rank": 1
        },
        {
            "text": "The full set of the COMPASS data set collected with a muon beam between 2002 and 2011 has been used. ",
            "section": "Z c (3900)",
            "paragraph_rank": 2,
            "section_rank": 1
        },
        {
            "text": "An upper limit for the ratio BR( Z \u00b1 c (3900) \u2192 J /\u03c8\u03c0 \u00b1 ) \u00d7 \u03c3 \u03b3 N\u2192Z \u00b1 c (3900)N /\u03c3 \u03b3 N\u2192 J /\u03c8 N of 3.7 \u00d7 10 \u22123 has been established at the confidence level of 90%. ",
            "section": "Z c (3900)",
            "paragraph_rank": 2,
            "section_rank": 1
        },
        {
            "text": "E-mail addresses: Andrea.Bressan@cern.ch (A. Bressan), Alexey.Guskov@cern.ch (A. Guskov), Fabienne.Kunne@cern.ch (F. Kunne).",
