        {
            "text": "It has been interpreted as a tetraquark state [3][4][5][6], although other explanations like a molecular state [7][8][9][10][11], a cusp effect [12] and an initial-single-pion-emission mechanism [13] were also proposed. ",
            "section": "Z c (3900)",
            "paragraph_rank": 5,
            "section_rank": 1,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
